title: Rickrolling Anniversary
alt: Want to feel old? The 'want to feel old?' factoid meme dates back to around 2011, closer to the Bush/Kerry election than to today.
transcript:
[Cueball and Megan are walking.]
Cueball: This month marks ten years since the peak of the Rickrolling phenomenon.[In a frame-less panel they keep walking.]
Megan: Seriously?
Megan: Wow. Happy anniversary, I guess.[They keep walking silently, beat panel.][And they walk on.]
Cueball: We've known each other for so long.
Megan: We really have.
